With [Respring Assistant], a basic utility tweak, you can:
1. Restart your SpringBoard QUICKLY, making installed tweaks work as expected;
2. Refresh App Icons EASILY, making your hidden app icons appear again;
3. Restore hosts file NORMALLY, solving network problems caused by broken hosts file.

[快速注销器] 是个越狱基础工具，帮您：
1. 快速重启SpringBoard，注销设备，以让插件生效;
2. 一键刷新桌面的应用图标，解决插件安装后不显示图标的问题;
3. 一键恢复hosts到出厂状态，修复各种由于hosts文件导致的网络问题。

support all iOS versions(5.1.1~13.2.3), and all iOS devices(iPhone 4/4S/5/5S/5C/6/6+/6S/6S+/7/7+/SE/8/8+/X/XR/Xs/Max/11/11Pro)。支持所有iOS系统(5.1.1~13.2.3)版本及设备(包括iPhone 4/4S/5/5S/5C/6/6+/6S/6S+/7/7+/SE/8/8+/X/XR/Xs/Max/11/11Pro), iPad, iPod Touch. 完美兼容最新13.2.3越狱

